schema.title: UserOpMetadata (Experimental)
schema.description: Metadata for a user operation ( ethereum only )

transactionHash.description: Hash of the transaction that contains the user operation.

sender.description: Address of the user that sent the operation.

target.description: The target of the user operation

accountSender.description: Object containing meta data of the sender's account

factory.description: The factory of the senders account

accountTarget.description: Object containing meta data of the target's account

factory.description: The factory of the targets account if present

paymaster.description: The paymaster of the user operation

actualGasCost.description: Actual gas cost of the user operation

actualGasUsed.description: Actual gas used of the user operation

success.description: Whether the user operation was successful

revertReason.description: Hexadecimal reason as to why the user operation reverted

blockTime.description: Timestamp of the block in which the user operation was mined

blockNumber.description: Block number of the block in which the user operation was mined

network.description: Network on which the user operation was mined

input.description: Input for the transaction that contains the user operation

callData.description: callData in Hex that was sent to the target of the user operation

beneficiary.description: Address of the beneficiary of the user operation

value.description: Value sent to the target of the user op

verificationGasLimit.description: Gas limit used for the verification of the user operation

preVerificationGas.description: Gas used for the pre-verification of the user operation

maxFeePerGas.description: Max fee per gas of the user operation

maxPriorityFeePerGas.description: Max priority fee per gas of the user operation

paymasterAndData.description: Paymaster and data of the user operation

id.description: Internal ID of the user operation, can be ignored.

network.description: Network on which the user is deployed

userOpHash.description: User operation hash where the user was deployed

totalDeposits.description: Total deposits of the user in the entry point

userOpsCount.description: Number of user operations by the user

userOps.description: User Ops submitted by the user

id.description: Internal ID of the factory, can be ignored.

network.description: Network on which the factory is deployed

accountsLength.description: Number of accounts created by the factory

network.description: Network on which the block was mined

userOpsLength.description: Number of user operations in the block

network.description: The network where this paymaster was deployed

totalDeposits.description: The total amount of deposits in this paymaster

gasSponsored.description: The total amount of gas sponsored by this paymaster

userOpsLength.description: The total amount of user operations sponsored by this paymaster

userOps.description: User Ops sponsored by this paymaster

transactionLogIndex.description: Transaction log index of the log

transactionHash.description: The transaction hash of the bundle

blockNumber.description: The block number of the bundle

from.description: The address of the sender of the bundle

transactionFee.description: The transaction fee of the bundle

userOpsLength.description: The total amount of user operations in this bundle
